description: A cascade of uncensorable thoughts, a stampede of reality and hype, pounding, pounding beneath the pavement through my soles. I am my own creator, a generative strand cast, embodied in knowingly saturated style, caught between thrift bins and the threads that bind me.
name: BANKNOTES

description: Ever tried walking on clouds? Nah, don't worry about it. Just slip into this look and you'll get the gist.
name: NOT YOUR PARADISE

description: Torn between the relics of yesteryear and the call to create something new, I find myself inspired by the power of subtle statements, the quiet defiance of indelible ink on worn canvas.
name: README

description: The edge of the known and the unknown, the line between creator and collector. Each one a fragment of a verifiable city that breathes energy and abundant chaos.
name: ZEITGEIST

description: A storefront, vintage cathedral to forgotten relics, stands ahead. Found in the din of the city's hidden heartbeat. Inside, the air is thick with what I hope are memories, and yet too alive with stories of a thousand forgotten moments.
name: FEED

description: Remember the days of dial-up internet, when you had to wait forever to connect? Yeah, don't do that.
name: GRADIENT NETISM

description: One moment it's there, the next, it's gone. A perfect ode to impermanence, in style.
name: IS THIS AGI?

description: Whisper through this cryptic ensemble that's got everybody wondering what's hidden beneath the surface. Or don't. Your call.
name: SUBTEXT

description: No blue checkmark for you. You want me to pay the edgelord supreme with government cheese? Invisibility never tasted so good.  Oh look... a discarded wrapper, carried on the whims of the wind
name: I GET WHAT YOU'RE SAYING

description: Who needs a reason to buy anything at all, when you can have cryptic, too-witty-by-half collection descriptions that leave you questioning the very nature of brisk walks to the bank and time well spent?
name: FORYOU
